<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-2"><a href="#Positive_hijacks"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Positive hijacks</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-3"><a href="#Emotional_relearning"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">Emotional relearning</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="#See_also"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">See also</span></a></li>
